{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d13e45d6c","title":"中央文革调查组接见首都红代会在宁战士时的讲话","origin":"首都大专院校红代会华东联络站《华东通讯》第十期","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d829eee377","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"5d13e45d6c"}],"tags":[{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"65f109e920","name":"中央文革调查组"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"35faf23fed","type":"title","text":"中央文革调查组接见首都红代会在宁战士时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"e40a643444","type":"authors","text":"中央文革调查组","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"c4b502ab90","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿一日下午，中央文革江苏调查组接见了首都红代会大专院校在宁战士。总理秘书宋皋同志讲话要点如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"a1f412d4bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）南京文化大革命开展比较早，交大，南大都比较早，但形势较复杂；","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"f45c37943b","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）要研究解决五月十四日后南京争论的焦点是什么，要历史的唯物的研究；","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"e910ddc4a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）五月十四日张春桥同志讲话是中央肯定的；","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"8e4c017fee","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）如果都是造反派，为什么会出现这样的局面，有没有前台？有没有后台？有没有后台的黑后台？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"9bc24501a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）你们要宣传毛泽东思想，制止武斗，建立革命新秩序。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"},{"id":"dbe421daba","type":"paragraph","text":" （首都大专院校红代会华东联络站《华东通讯》第十期）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c"}],"page":{"id":"8b7c8adaa2","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}